org.cef.callback

Interface CefSchemeHandlerFactory


  • public interface CefSchemeHandlerFactory
    Class that creates CefResourceHandler instances for handling scheme requests. The methods of this class will always be called on the IO thread.(此类创建用于处理scheme请求的CefResourceHandler实例。此类的方法将始终在IO线程上调用。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      CefResourceHandler create(CefBrowser browser, CefFrame frame, java.lang.String schemeName, CefRequest request)
      Return a new resource handler instance to handle the request or NULL to allow default handling of the request.(返回一个新的资源处理程序实例来处理请求，或者返回NULL以允许默认处理请求。)

    • Method Detail

      • create

        CefResourceHandler create(CefBrowser browser,
                          CefFrame frame,
                          java.lang.String schemeName,
                          CefRequest request)
        Return a new resource handler instance to handle the request or NULL to allow default handling of the request.(返回一个新的资源处理程序实例来处理请求，或者返回NULL以允许默认处理请求。)
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser, or NULL if the request did not originate from a browser window (for example, if the request came from CefURLRequest).(browser-相应的浏览器，如果请求不是来自浏览器窗口，则为NULL（例如，如果请求来自CefURLRequest）。)
        frame - The frame generating the event, or NULL if the request did not originate from a browser window (for example, if the request came from CefURLRequest). Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame ，如果请求不是来自浏览器窗口，则为NULL（例如，如果请求来自CefURLRequest）。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        schemeName - Name of the scheme being created.(schemeName-正在创建的scheme的名称。)
        request - The request itself. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(request-请求本身。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
